headline: Erie Indemnity (ERIE): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: Over the past six months, Erie Indemnity’s shares (currently trading at $359.82) have posted a disappointing 7.8% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 6.4% gain. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
